ators. Hopefully, Generalized Differential Calculus and\nthe developments presented in this paper, may be of interest to those working\nin Analysis, Applied Mathematics, Geometry and Physics.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 30 Apr 2022 00:09:22 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-05-03"}
