r Energy-Delay-Squared Product at 50 microsecond time epochs,\nreaching 32% power efficiencies when operated with 1 microsecond DVFS\ntechnologies.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 30 Apr 2022 01:06:52 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-05-03"}
