 allows for reliable adaption\nof ASs to new information in their operational environment.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 30 Apr 2022 03:46:03 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 1 Jun 2022 00:04:15 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-06-02"}
