heres of L dwarfs, and for the first time\nobservationally establishes their emergence and sedimentation between effective\ntemperatures of $\\approx$2000 K and $\\approx$1300 K, respectively.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 30 Apr 2022 05:50:51 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-06-08"}
