ork with a maximum access distance of\n300m. Conclusion: What stands out from this method is that the combination of\nthe modified feeder route design model and algorithms is feasible.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 29 Apr 2022 19:46:56 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-05-11"}
